  "description": "<p><strong>Company Name:</strong> ALTAF TECHNOLOGIES SERVICES PTE. LTD.<br />\n<strong>Job Title:</strong> Carpenter<br />\n<strong>Industry:</strong> Construction<br />\n<strong>Job Type:</strong> Full-Time</p><p><strong>Job\nDescription / Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>·       \nCarry out construction carpentry works including\nformwork, fixing, and installation</p><p>·       \nMeasure, cut, and assemble wood and other\nmaterials based on drawings and instructions</p><p>·       \nInstall doors, frames, partitions, and other\nwooden structures</p><p>·       \nRepair and maintain existing carpentry\nstructures at construction sites</p><p>·       \nFollow safety regulations and site supervisor\ninstructions</p><p>·       \nEnsure work quality meets project and site\nrequirements</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>·       \nMinimum <strong>3\nyears of relevant experience</strong> as a construction carpenter</p><p>·       \nExperience working on construction sites</p><p>·       \nKnowledge of carpentry tools, equipment, and\nmaterials</p><p>·       \nAble to work independently and as part of a team</p><p>·       \nPhysically fit for construction work</p>",
